\c 2
\s Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* eBokimi
\p
\v 1 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasisenyuka isuka eGiligali isiya eBokimi\x + 2.5.\x*, yathi: Ngalenyusa lisuka eGibhithe, ngaliletha elizweni engalifungela oyihlo, njalo ngathi: Kangiyikwephula isivumelwano sami\x + Dute. 31.16.\x* lani kuze kube sephakadeni.
\v 2 Lani-ke kaliyikwenza isivumelwano labahlali balelilizwe\x + Dute. 7.2.\x*, lizadiliza amalathi abo\x + Dute. 12.3.\x*. Kodwa kalililalelanga ilizwi lami\x + 2.20; 1.29,32,33.\x*. Kuyini lokhu elikwenzileyo?
\v 3 Ngakho lami ngathi: Kangiyikuzixotsha elifeni phambi kwenu, kodwa zizakuba \add njengameva\add* enhlangothini\x + Nani 33.55. Josh. 23.13.\x* zenu, labonkulunkulu bazo\x + 3.6.\x* babe ngumjibila kini\x + Eks. 23.33.\x*.
\v 4 Kwasekusithi lapho ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* isikhulume lamazwi kubo bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli, abantu baphakamisa ilizwi labo bakhala inyembezi.
\v 5 Basebebiza ibizo laleyondawo \add ngokuthi\add* yiBokimi, bayihlabela iN\nd kosi\nd* lapho.
\s Ukufa kukaJoshuwa
\p
\v 6 Kwathi uJoshuwa esebayekele abantu bahamba\x + 2.9, Josh. 24.28,29,30,31.\x*, abantwana bakoIsrayeli bahamba, ngulowo lalowo waya elifeni lakhe ukudla ilifa lelizwe.
\v 7 Abantu basebeyikhonza iN\nd kosi\nd* kuzo zonke izinsuku zikaJoshuwa, lazo zonke izinsuku zabadala abasala bephila emva kukaJoshuwa, ababewubonile wonke umsebenzi omkhulu weN\nd kosi\nd* eyayiwenzele uIsrayeli.
\v 8 UJoshuwa indodana kaNuni, inceku yeN\nd kosi\nd*, wafa-ke, eleminyaka elikhulu letshumi.
\v 9 Basebemngcwabela emngceleni welifa lakhe eThiminathi-Heresi entabeni yakoEfrayimi\x + Josh. 24.30. Josh. 24.33.\x*, enyakatho kwentaba iGahashi.
\v 10 Njalo lalesosizukulwana sabuthelwa kuboyise. Kwasekusukuma esinye isizukulwana emva kwabo esasingayazi iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Eks. 5.2. 1 Sam. 2.12. 1 Lan. 28.9. Jer. 9.3,24; 22.16. Gal. 4.8. 1 Thes. 4.5. 2 Thes. 1.8. Tit. 1.16.\x* njalo lomsebenzi eyayiwenzele uIsrayeli.
\s Okubi kukaIsrayeli
\p
\v 11 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, bakhonza oBhali.
\v 12 Batshiya iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Dute. 31.16.\x*, uNkulunkulu waboyise, eyabakhupha elizweni leGibhithe, balandela abanye onkulunkulu\x + Dute. 6.14.\x*, kubonkulunkulu bezizwe ezazibazingelezele, bakhothama\x + 2.17,19. Eks. 20.3,5.\x* kibo, bayithukuthelisa\x + Dute. 31.29.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 13 Bayidela iN\nd kosi\nd*, bakhonza uBhali \w laboAshitarothi\w**\x + 2.11; 3.7; 10.6. 1 Sam. 7.4. Hlab. 106.36.\x*.
\v 14 Ngakho ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* lwavutha kuIsrayeli\x + 2.20; 3.8. Hlab. 106.40,41.\x*, yabanikela esandleni sabaphangi ababaphangayo\x + 2.20; 3.8. Hlab. 106.40,41.\x*; yabathengisa esandleni sezitha zabo inhlangothi zonke\x + Dute. 32.30.\x*, ukuze bangabe besaba lakho ukuma phambi kwazo\x + Levi 26.37. Josh. 7.12,13.\x*.
\v 15 Loba bephuma besiya ngaphi, isandla seN\nd kosi\nd* samelana labo ngokubi, njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\nd* lanjengokufunga kweN\nd kosi\nd* kibo\x + Levi 26. Dute. 28.\x*, njalo bacindezeleka kakhulu.
\s Ukumiswa kwabahluleli
\p
\v 16 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimisa abahluleli\x + 3.9,15. 1 Sam. 12.11. Seb. 13.20.\x* ababophula esandleni salabo ababaphangayo.
\v 17 Kanti kababalalelanga labahluleli babo, kodwa baphinga ngokulandela abanye onkulunkulu\x + Eks. 34.15. Hlu. 8.33.\x*, bakhothama kibo; baphambuka masinyane endleleni oyise ababehamba kuyo\x + Dute. 9.12.\x*, belalela imilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd*. Bona kabenzanga njalo.
\v 18 Lalapho iN\nd kosi\nd* ibamisela abahluleli, iN\nd kosi\nd* yayilomahluleli\x + Josh. 1.5.\x*, yabophula esandleni sezitha zabo zonke izinsuku zikamahluleli; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yazisola\x + Hlab. 106.45. Jona 3.10. Gen. 6.6. Dute. 32.36. 2 Lan. 7.14. Jer. 18.8; 26.3. Hlu. 10.16.\x* ngenxa yokububula kwabo ngenxa yalabo ababacindezelayo lababahlukuluzayo\x + Eks. 2.24; 6.5.\x*.
\v 19 Kwasekusithi ekufeni kukamahluleli\x + 3.12; 4.1; 8.33.\x*, babuyela emuva baxhwala okwedlula oyise, ngokulandela abanye onkulunkulu, ngokubakhonza langokubakhothamela; kabalahlanga okwemisebenzi yabo lokwendlela yabo yenkani.
\p
\v 20 Ngakho ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* lwavutha kuIsrayeli\x + 2.14.\x*, yathi: Ngoba lesisizwe seqe isivumelwano sami engasilaya oyise\x + Dute. 17.2.\x*, kasilalelanga ilizwi lami,
\v 21 lami kangisayikuxotsha loba ngubani elifeni phambi kwabo ezizweni uJoshuwa azitshiya ekufeni kwakhe\x + Josh. 23.13. Hlu. 2.3. Josh. 13.6.\x*,
\v 22 ukuze ngihlole ngazo uIsrayeli\x + 3.1,4.\x*\x + Eks. 15.25.\x* ukuthi bazagcina yini indlela yeN\nd kosi\nd* ukuhamba kuyo njengaboyise ba\add yi\add*gcina, kumbe hatshi.
\v 23 Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* yaziyekela lezozizwe, ukuze ingazixotshi elifeni masinyane, njalo kayizinikelanga esandleni sikaJoshuwa.